data.description: PRICED TO SALE! NO HOA! Spacious 4 bed/2.5 ba/2-car garage home on unfinshed basement in sought-after Cooper/McConnell/Archer school district. Welcoming rocking chair front porch leads to foyer entry & separate Fml living & dining rooms & spacious kitchen w/bkfst rm & walk-in pantry open to fireside family room. 4 generous bedrooms upstairs. Storage space galore. Huge, privacy-fenced backyard w/covered patio Home is clean inside & out & move-in ready! New roof 2015 & HVAC 2018. IDEAL LOCATION close to GREAT schools & parks.
